title: Brian Auger's Oblivion Express First 5 albums
description: First 5 albums by this great band.  Includes the great album Second Wind with Alex Ligertwood on vocals who used the tune "Truth" for his audition for the Jeff Beck Group.  Legend has it that Max Middleton, the keyboardist has photographic memory, transcribed the melody and changes that became the hit, "Situation".  Check it out.  It&#039;s the same tune.
